normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2粒鐘好快就過 四場打鬥都做得好 (WW 港灣 對超人 最後打 boss)<br />\n打鬥模式都 AVG 果邊多射野招招招唔同 <br />\n呢邊好多都係一野轟落去場面 拍出來好實在同有震撼 <br />\n就算好唔過 AVG1 都一定好過 AVG2<br />\n成套野個問題在於句 You cant save the world alone 到<br />\n如果冇呢句野套戲就好 make sense: 有外星人黎 打唔嬴 搵幫手 END<br />\n而家一個超高 Lv 既人帶班低 Lv 既打副本升 Lv <br />\n當係 warm up同團結下班人<br />\n始終 Flash Aquaman 同 Batman 能力方面都有得強化落去<br />\n我估下次打 injustice 奸角果邊有方法牽制超人"},{"pid":"0003306b59d0939917854e6b598c51d8cf4c7bc1","tid":476942,"uid":111149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T00:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>特技完勝marvel</blockquote><br />\n超人遮鬍鬚cg世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://i0.kym-cdn.com/news_feeds/icons/mobile/000/028/954/adb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.kym-cdn.com%2Fnews_feeds%2Ficons%2Fmobile%2F000%2F028%2F954%2Fadb.jpg&h=4c07e393&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a472ec83b4efeb312474b222ee08051bb548c8","tid":476942,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T00:55:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>特技完勝marvel</blockquote><br />\n超人遮鬍鬚cg世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://i0.kym-cdn.com/news_feeds/icons/mobile/000/028/954/adb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.kym-cdn.com%2Fnews_feeds%2Ficons%2Fmobile%2F000%2F028%2F954%2Fadb.jpg&h=4c07e393&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n猩空堀起"},{"pid":"cd6d6aad3fb32ea344b8018b5e836c490af246ed","tid":476942,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:04:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>抵啦<br />\n唔撚一早出陽光正能量撚超人<br />\n係都要扮獨樹一格清泉又要戴頭盔加笑位<br />\nmarketing時出時唔出最出名果個超人<br />\n為左補番個角色形象犧牲個故事同拎其他主角襯托<br />\nbatman只係太監仔加司機完全冇同超人平起平坐feel</blockquote><br />\n今集突然變左打交會笑既超人仲怪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪JOSS囉屌</blockquote><br />\n今日稍早，導演扎克.史奈德 (Zack Snyder) 的兒子傑特.伊林 (Jett Elin) 通過社群平台 Vero 分享了自己對《正義聯盟》的短評：<br />\n<br />\n「認真的說，我確實很享受這部電影，雖然很明顯這不是它該有的模樣，因為華納兄弟影業的介入以及強性喜劇。<br />\n<br />\n片長是我對這部電影最大的不滿，一個需要花比較長時間講述的故事在片刻結束。但它還是一部值得觀賞的電影，而且很推薦。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/190030_ea7130fc8196776d8756f83e7c7b4668.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F190030_ea7130fc8196776d8756f83e7c7b4668.jpg&h=513ff9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇zack個仔咁講 應該係wb要求joss改<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\njoss比wb擺上台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實都明wb點解咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只能夠話好可惜冇得睇原本既三部曲終章</blockquote><br />\nWb班高層d眼光同世人應該唔同<br />\nWw好多人鐘意個場攻村劇，好似話本來想剪走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdc5923ad84f3c351274597f89cbb77c96026b7","tid":476942,"uid":149201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T08:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>抵啦<br />\n唔撚一早出陽光正能量撚超人<br />\n係都要扮獨樹一格清泉又要戴頭盔加笑位<br />\nmarketing時出時唔出最出名果個超人<br />\n為左補番個角色形象犧牲個故事同拎其他主角襯托<br />\nbatman只係太監仔加司機完全冇同超人平起平坐feel</blockquote><br />\n今集突然變左打交會笑既超人仲怪</blockquote