F2017%2F11%2F23%2F190030_ea7130fc8196776d8756f83e7c7b4668.jpg&h=513ff9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇zack個仔咁講 應該係wb要求joss改<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\njoss比wb擺上台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實都明wb點解咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只能夠話好可惜冇得睇原本既三部曲終章</blockquote><br />\nWb班高層d眼光同世人應該唔同<br />\nWw好多人鐘意個場攻村劇，好似話本來想剪走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWB班高層真係智障，BVS衰過鑊仲今次夠膽死大CUT</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返去整賓尼兔啦"},{"pid":"eb4397c6b62399be096ccd5ec9042b51fabf44a3","tid":476942,"uid":59919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"BOSS太弱,比超人屌打"},{"pid":"5c3deaa5542024535fe0c1d13aa9d2944ff3e0f8","tid":476942,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T12:22:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BOSS太弱,比超人屌打</blockquote><br />\n我唔覺得nerf角色就一定好睇<br />\n超人設定上就係咁屈<br />\n都係做返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42f562ab5849cde008da05e2138b26af42ecde4","tid":476942,"uid":82743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T12:26:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>BOSS太弱,比超人屌打</blockquote><br />\n我唔覺得nerf角色就一定好睇<br />\n超人設定上就係咁屈<br />\n都係做返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋通常漫畫超人唔係輸比舊石就係輸比自己低智商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次對面果個一來以為超人死左唔會出黎二來都唔係有咩智商...緊係比超人屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}